# TC14: StopCharging2
# Precondition setup: StandbyMode, charging in progress
# Action: press start button once
# Expected: no change because start is ignored while charging.
power
battery 50
charge
expect power on
expect mode StandbyMode
expect charging on
expect battery 60
expect motor stopped
expect cleaner off
start
expect power on
expect mode StandbyMode
expect charging on
expect battery 60
expect motor stopped
expect cleaner off
expect cleanerMode off
exit
